    {
      "block_id": "1978-06-paragraph-c8b5c3d4f0-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "Len Englund now has a scrapbook and is looking for someone to bring it up to date. I know if you were asked to help you probably would\u2013\u2013any volunteers??",
